            <div id="DIVContent" class="yywh"><p align="justify"
                                                 style="margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;text-align:justify;">
                    <span style="font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span
                            style="font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;">俗话说：</span><span
                            style="font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;">“七十不留宿，八十不留饭，九十不留坐”，可见老年人一旦上了岁数，稍不注意，就容易出现问题。常见的突发意外事件多为心脑血管方面的疾病，但也有相当多一部分是因为跌倒导致骨折，多为髋部骨折，它有“终末骨折”的骇人称号。近日我院骨二科在张国强主任带领下成功为两位高龄髋部骨折患者实施了半髋关节置换手术。如今两位患者病情平稳，已下床自主活动。</span>
                </p>
                <p align="justify" style="text-align:center;margin-left:0pt;text-indent:0pt;">
                    <span style="font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;"><img src="${ctxPath}/images/2016102617284261.JPG"
                                                                          alt=""/></span>
                </p>
                <p align="justify" style="text-align:center;margin-left:0pt;text-indent:0pt;">
	<span style="font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;"><img src="${ctxPath}/images/201611141904542.JPG" alt=""/><br/>
</span>
                </p>
                <p align="justify" style="text-align:center;margin-left:0pt;text-indent:0pt;">
                    <span style="font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;"> </span>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <span style="font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;83</span><span
                            style="font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;">岁的老人近期下大雪不慎摔倒致左股骨粗隆间粉碎性骨折，经过半髋关节置换术后，现已可拄拐下床活动，恢复良好。</span>
                </p>
                <div style="text-align:center;">
                    <img src="${ctxPath}/images/201611141904542.JPG" alt=""/>
                </div>
                <p>
                    <br/>
                </p>
                <p align="justify" style="text-align:center;margin-left:0pt;text-indent:0pt;">
                    <span style="font-family:SimSun;font-size:16px;"> </span>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;88</span><span
                            style="font-size:16px;">岁的老奶奶在家里不慎摔倒致左股骨颈基底部骨折，为其实施髋关节置换手术后，恢复平稳。</span>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <span> </span>
                </p>
                <p style="text-align:left;">
                    <span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:16px;">这两例高龄患者均为非常规的髋关节置换术，前者为粗隆间粉碎性骨折，术中需要固定大粗隆；后者股骨颈基底部骨折，骨折累及小粗隆，手术的话，均会延长手术时间，增加术中出血机会，麻醉风险也会加大。面对这样的情况，骨二科敢于挑战困难病例及复杂手术，成立三年多来已成功地为</span><span
                            style="font-size:16px;">200</span><span style="font-size:16px;">多名患者成功实施了髋关节置换手术，为广大股骨头坏死及高龄髋部骨折患者</span><span
                            style="line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;">解除了病痛。</span>
